import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"vagrant-overview"}}>{`Vagrant Overview`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="table" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="thead" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="thead">
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Action`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Command`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tbody" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`vagrant reload`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Vagrant `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="td">{`halt`}</MDXTag>{` followed by `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="td">{`up`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`vagrant up`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Start a Vagrant box`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`vagrant ssh`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Secret shell into a Vagrant box`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"vagrant-port-forwarding"}}>{`Vagrant Port Forwarding`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`To forward 80 => 8080 from Vagrant Box to host.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-ruby"}}>{`Vagrant.configure("2") do |config|
  # Other config
  config.vm.network "forwarded_port", guest: 80, guest_ip: "0.0.0.0", host: 8080, host_ip: "127.0.0.1"
end
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-ruby"}}>{`config.vm.provider 'virtualbox' do |vb|
  vb.customize ['modifyvm', :id, '--cableconnected1', 'on']
end
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
